Now, Every camera need calculate which item be touched. Though you don't touch the item, the 3D cemara think you touch the item.

```
auto camera = Camera::getVisitingCamera();
_selectedItem = this->getItemForTouch(touch, camera);
```

I think need use the camera mask.

```
auto camera = Camera::getVisitingCamera();
if((camera->getCameraFlag() & this->getCameraMask())!=0){
    _selectedItem = this->getItemForTouch(touch, camera);
}
```

